dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting AutoGuard Insurance. My name is Wayne Green. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Cheryl. How can I assist you today?
I'd like to file a new claim after a recent incident.
Of course, Cheryl. To assist you efficiently, could you please provide me with your policy number and the date of the incident in a day, month, year format?
My policy number is zero three two one four and the incident date is January five, two zero two two.
Thank you, Cheryl. I've noted the details. Is there any other information you'd like to add before we proceed with the claim?
No, that's all for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Cheryl. We'll start processing your claim right away. Thank you for reaching out to us. Have a great day!
